      "span_text": "Cellular BRCA1 forms a heterodimer with BRCA1-associated RING domain 1 (BARD1) (Wu et al., 1996) , which promotes the repair of double-stranded DNA breaks through homologous recombination [CITATION_1] and contributes to the DNA-damage-induced G2/M checkpoint (Xu et al., 2001) ."
